1
00:00:00,240 --> 00:00:03,839
[SPEAKER_01] U ime Oca i Sina i Duha Svetoga, Amen.

2
00:00:08,320 --> 00:00:11,599
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodine, mi te sada molimo da ti isporiš naše srce.

3
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:27,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje smo došli da slavimo tvoje ime.

4
00:00:28,879 --> 00:00:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si došao da te slavimo.

5
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:36,159
[SPEAKER_01] Slavu tvoj.

6
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tko mi je na?

7
00:00:39,359 --> 00:00:42,560
[SPEAKER_01] Tko kaču sa tobom?

8
00:00:43,759 --> 00:00:46,079
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja sam tvoj.

9
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:51,520
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam tvoj.

10
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:55,920
[SPEAKER_01] Sveto mi je na miru.

11
00:00:57,200 --> 00:01:00,399
[SPEAKER_01] Da je pojoj ljubavni.

12
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:03,280
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja sam tvoj.

13
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam tvoj.

14
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:12,560
[SPEAKER_01] Smahu poji.

15
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:14,240
[SPEAKER_01] Svagu vodu i vremena, vi kaču sa krvava, jer ja sam tvoj.

16
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam tvoj.

17
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:32,480
[SPEAKER_01] Sve što je u meni daje tvojoj ljubavi, jer ja sam tvoj.

18
00:20:04,799 --> 00:20:22,559
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, priznajem, klanja nam se, bez tebe gurmaju se.

19
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nedostojno za nas predano.

20
00:30:07,519 --> 00:30:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjek je i bol i znak svega usvišenja.

21
00:30:13,839 --> 00:30:18,160
[SPEAKER_01] Sva slava nek je tvoje i vedu.

22
00:30:24,079 --> 00:30:25,200
[SPEAKER_01] I vedu.

23
00:30:31,119 --> 00:30:32,160
[SPEAKER_00] I vedu.

24
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] Sad probudi u nama, sad probudi u nama, sad probudi u nama, češnju za to boo.

